      "widgets_values": [
        " # OmniVoice Empity Narrator\n\n  \n  OmniVoice also supports narrator-free generation.\n  If you set narrator to `none`, the model can generate using its own native default voice behavior instead of cloning.\n\n  The `instruct` field is strongest when no narrator/reference is provided.\n  In that mode, OmniVoice uses the instruction to design the voice directly.\n  When narrator/reference cloning is active, the instruction still affects the result, but usually much more weakly because the model prioritizes the provided voice identity."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
